data.description: Opportunity to build out your dream kitchen! expansive vacation like home! This will be a Short Sale. Vacant lot to the right of  driveway is not included but can be purchased from the owner of the land.  4 bed 2.5 bath w/ 2 bonus rooms and finished basement. Huge bonus is the 4 seasons room equipped with bar and sink, the perfect spot to entertain family and friends. Work from home at ease w/ this large office w/ French doors! Spacious living room with fireplace and formal dining room with bay windows. Sizeable bedrooms on the 2nd floor with so much storage and closet space. Two-tier TREX deck and HUGE BONUS an above ground pool! Two Additional sheds to store all your outdoor gear. Oversized 2.5 car garage w/ workstation and storage cabinets. Roof 2019! New Furnace and A/C 2021!  HWH 201
